    sections: [
      { heading: 'Mat shoes', body: [
        'Lightweight, flexible, designed for the cheer-stunt and tumbling track.',
        'Sized to the foot. Replace at the end of every season.',
      ]},
      { heading: 'Bracing', body: [
        'Ankle braces for kids with prior sprains. Sized by ankle circumference.',
        'Wrist supports for tumbling drills. The coach will tell you when to add them.',
